data.meta_description: Princess Astrid is the second daughter of King Olav V of Norway and his wife, Princess Martha of Sweden. She is the older sister of King Harald V of orway and younger sister of Princess Ragnhild of Norway. As she is the great granddaughter of Edward VII of the United Kingdom, she is in line of succession to the British throne. She is a second cousin of Elizabeth II and also first cousin to Badouin of Belgium and his successor Albert II of Belgium
